# CEChecker — Privacy Policy

**Last updated: April 2026**

## Overview

CEChecker is a Chrome extension that scans web pages for circular economy terminology. This policy explains how the extension handles data.

## Data collection

CEChecker does **not** collect, store, transmit or share any personal data or browsing data.

## How it works

- When you click **Scan this page**, the extension reads the visible text content of the current tab locally on your device
- Matching terms are highlighted directly on the page
- No data leaves your device
- No data is sent to any server
- No analytics or tracking of any kind is used

## Permissions

| Permission | Reason |
|---|---|
| `activeTab` | To access the current tab's page content when you initiate a scan |
| `scripting` | To scan page text and inject highlights onto matching terms |

Both permissions are only activated when you click the scan button. The extension does not run in the background or access any tab you have not explicitly scanned.

